# Design tokens & UI usage docs (always consult)

When working on UI, styling, theming, layout, or component patterns in this repo:

- Read `docs/design-system/ASSONA-DESIGN-TOKENS.md` before making token-related decisions.
- Use `docs/design-system/USAGE-EXAMPLES.md` as the default reference for how to apply tokens in components.

Hard rules:
- Do not introduce hardcoded hex/rgb/hsl colors if a token exists.
- Prefer semantic token variables (`var(--color-...)`) over raw palette tokens unless the codebase standard requires otherwise.
- Keep dark mode parity: verify any UI change works in both themes.

